Meet Anthony Genovese of Brookfield Properties, one of our 2024 REBNY Fellows. Anthony hopes to continue his career and grow young talent in the real estate field addressing challenges, advancing typical building operations and to advance technology and energy efficiency innovation in our buildings. All of the Fellows come from different sectors of the real estate industry, but they all share a common goal of building their leadership skills and taking their career to the next level. Watch out for posts highlighting more of the 2024 Fellows in the coming weeks! And thanks as always to our partners at Coro New York Leadership Center for helping us make this program possible. Learn more about the program and the fellows: https://lnkd.in/ecfDqYBd
